// hato.krs.style
// The hato API consumes most third-party SaaS, so the auto side-split (by
// consuming-hub position) groups them all on one side. Pin the shared identity
// proxy to the opposite side so the front-door auth dependency reads apart from
// the data integrations (#1728: `column` picks the side for [external]).

#CloudflareAccess {
  column: right;
}
